- [STM8 Software Development Tools](http://www.st.com/content/st_com/en/products/development-tools/software-development-tools/stm8-software-development-tools.html?querycriteria=productId=SC2108)
- [How to Program STMicro STM8S $1 Board in Linux](http://www.cnx-software.com/2015/04/13/how-to-program-stm8s-1-board-in-linux/)
